      the specific UI slot where the bandage was stored","comment":null,"color":{"r":0.0,"g":0.0,"b":0.0,"a":1.0},"guid":"8e9a331b-c8b2-4629-a106-15758fffea51","$version":"A","$type":"Unity.VisualScripting.GraphGroup"},{"position":{"xMin":-859.0,"yMin":1097.0,"xMax":247.0,"yMax":1483.0},"label":"case
